message: Since symfony/serializer 6.4: Passing a "Doctrine\Common\Annotations\AnnotationReader" instance as argument 1 to "Symfony\Component\Serializer\Mapping\Loader\AttributeLoader::__construct()" is deprecated, pass null or omit the parameter instead.
